                local public <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">servants</ENAMEX>, especially the <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</NUMEX> responders: fire, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">police</ENAMEX>, emergency
