                bottom, and <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">99</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">elevators</ENAMEX>. Generally, <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">elevators originating</ENAMEX> in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">lobby</ENAMEX> ran to "sky
