            <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">Stairwells A</ENAMEX> and C ran from the <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">110th</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">floor</ENAMEX> to the raised mezzanine level of the
