                of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">WTC</ENAMEX> or individual <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">companies</ENAMEX>, (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">3</ENAMEX>) volunteer <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">civilians</ENAMEX> who ran to the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">WTC</ENAMEX> after
