            Several factors influenced the evacuation on <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">September 11</TIMEX>. It was aided greatly by
                changes made by the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Port Authority</ENAMEX> in response to the <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1993</TIMEX> bombing and by the
                training of both <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Port Authority</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">personnel</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">civilians</ENAMEX> after that time. Stairwells
