            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Command</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Control</ENAMEX> within <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">First Responder Agencies</ENAMEX>.
            
            For a unified incident management system to succeed, each <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participant</ENAMEX> must have
                <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">command</ENAMEX> and control of its own <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">units</ENAMEX> and adequate internal communications. This was
